Traffic-bot is an AI system designed to handle traffic-related queries using Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) techniques. It processes traffic regulation documents, creates vector embeddings, and utilizes a language model to provide accurate and timely responses. The system features automated data updates and optimized architecture for scalability. It integrates with Chainlit for a conversational interface, making it user-friendly and efficient.
